  "extension": {
    "lang": "EN",
    "description": "<p>The Harmonised Index of Consumer Prices (HICP)\u202fmeasures price changes\u202fof\u202fvarious consumer goods and services\u202fover time\u202f(inflation). The index\u202fmeasures\u202fprice changes\u202fin relation to\u202fa\u202fbase year.\u202fData are\u202favailable\u202fwith 2 decimals for the aggregates and\u202f1 or 2 decimals for countries.</p>",
